data.body:
During a porting my games to Android find a bug. Sometimes game freezes at this loop:

while (TouchPanel.IsGestureAvailable)
                    {
                        GestureSample gesture = TouchPanel.ReadGesture();
                    }
At WP,Windows,Linux game works well!

Temporary replaced this code with my own, based on TouchPanel.GetState() with manual tracking.

Add support for the ColorWriteEnable render state to the MGFX parser.

```
ColorWriteEnable = Red | Green | Blue | Alpha;
ColorWriteEnable = Blue | Red;
ColorWriteEnable = None;
ColorWriteEnable = All;
```
